                20 of
                the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to the health of students generally, so as to require
                the
                Department of Education, in consultation with the Department of Behavioral Health and Developmental
                Disabilities and others, to develop guidelines for the use of telehealth services in public schools to
                provide mental health and behavioral health services to students at school or during any school related
                function; to define the term "telehealth"; to provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting laws;
                and
                for other purposes.</p>
